description:
Why did God touch the Egyptians property and livestock in the fifth plague? Did He want them to change their loyalty from Hathor to the good God of the Hebrews? Hear the amazing story of the sixth plague of the boils. How did this disaster affect Pharaoh? What can we learn about this plague from its description in the Destruction of Mankind found in the tomb of Seti I in the Valley of the Kings?

Join Francois du Plessis as he tours ancient sites to reveal lessons and details from the story of the Exodus.
